<div itemprop="description" class="job_listing-description job-overview col-md-12 col-sm-12">
<h2 class="widget-title widget-title--job_listing-top job-overview-title">Overview</h2>
<p>LOOKING FOR A GREAT HELPER &#8211; We are a French-American family. If the family you work for is relocating or you are a finished contract, and would like to join a nice household, please contact me. We have another helper from Ilocano. Each helper have their own rooms and one shared bathroom. Cooking is permitted in my house, use of fridge. No curfew, no crazy hours (different work hours). Salary is 4500 hkd + 1000 hkd food allowance. Will pay extra for someone with good references ( they are a must). Important to me:</p>
<ul>
<li>Good easy relationship with children (mine are 3 and 5)</li>
<li>Willing to work with another helper (and driver)</li>
<li>Good cleaning skills</li>
<li>Simple cooking (especially breakfast: eggs)</li>
<li>Saturday off</li>
</ul>
<p class="job_tags">Tagged as: Child care, Housekeeping</p>
